SUMMARY:CFMA Cajun Jam
DESCRIPTION:Vermilionville's weekly Cajun Jam Saturday afternoons 1-3 PM is led by some of the area's finest musicians. The free jam is held in the Performance Center and is open to all skill levels-beginner to professional. Admission is free but does not include entry to the park.
URL:https://bayouvermiliondistrict.org/event/cfma-cajun-jam/2026-05-30/
LOCATION:Vermilionville\, 300 Fisher Road\, Lafayette\, LA\, 70508\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music,Special Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bayouvermiliondistrict.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cajunjam3.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Bayou Vermilion District":MAILTO:marketing@bayouvermiliondistrict.org
END:VEVENT
