SUMMARY:Homeschool Days at Vermilionville
DESCRIPTION:The last Wednesday of each month is Homeschool Day at Vermilionville — homeschooling families get a discount on visits to the village! Come enjoy a self-guided tour and an optional rain garden tour at 11:30 AM. Admission: age 5-17: $6; 18+ $10.
URL:https://bayouvermiliondistrict.org/event/homeschool-days-at-vermilionville/2026-05-27/
LOCATION:Vermilionville\, 300 Fisher Road\, Lafayette\, LA\, 70508\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bayouvermiliondistrict.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Chief-sitting-bear.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Bayou Vermilion District":MAILTO:marketing@bayouvermiliondistrict.org
